features: Modern Design: The black and white crossover design makes the outdoor rugs an excellent choice for decks and patios，as its sleek and contemporary design will add more interest to your outdoor house. Reversible outdoor rugs have two sides available, so you can flip them over if either side becomes soiled or damaged. Because the front and back are different patterns, you can have two different designs in one purchase, saving you the hassle of buying or carrying more patio rugs.

Sturdy And Durable: Because the outdoor plastic rug is made from durable virgin polypropylene, they are weather resistant, so whether you live in damp or dusty areas, the plastic rugs will stand up to the rigors of daily use and the weather and won't quickly rot or tear. And with a durable coating resists fading caused by sunlight or chlorine exposure, maintaining its original appearance for years. You can leave it out in the sun without worrying about fading colors.

100% Recyclable Plastic: This eco-friendly outdoor carpet is made from recyclable plastic straws and is latex-free. This outdoor carpet is breathable and minimizes any adverse effects on the grass underneath it. Therefore, your garden will stay as put if you use the patio carpet on the grass for a long time. Moreover, it is non-slip, so it will stay still in place.

Easy To Clean - This waterproof outdoor rug require minimal maintenance, and when it's time to clean, soap or just a water rinse is all that's needed to keep them clean and fresh, without the need for scrubbing, vacuuming, or any elaborate cleaning process.

Take It Anywhere: The lightweight, soft design makes carrying the rug to different locations easy. The package includes a high-quality clutch bag you can fold and store in your car or RV, so it's always ready.Use it as rv mat, deck mat, picnic rug, camping rug, tent carpet, porch rug, balcony rug, indoor outdoor rug, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great outdoor rug for price!
reviews.reviewText: This rug looks great on our back patio, especially for the price. It's a great size (we put two chairs, a table, and our fire pit on it) and it looks really nice. The pattern and color was true to the picture. The only thing worth noting is that it comes all folded up so there are a lot of creases when you unfold it. That's not a huge deal to me, I haven't tried to smooth it out yet so I'm not sure what would work best for that.
